10009076_ASM_F_Main_v_T_T_TF_T_T_T_F_T
ActivityInitial -> Initialize watchdog variable to 0U -> Pet the Watchdog using RTE call -> Declare Local variable to store SSM state and Initialize RteCallRet to 1U ->
Is ASM_V_State_t not equal to ASM_INITIALISED? = True -> Read Master time reference value using Rte calll -> Is RteCallRet equals 0U? = True ->

Is ASM_V_State_t equals ASM_INITIALISED? = True -> Read SSM State using RTE call and Update RteCallRet -> Is RteCallRet equals 0U? = True ->
Is SSM in Running vision Mode? -> Read latest data from HCA and Update RteCallRet -> Is RteCallRet equals 0U? = False -> Read latest Data from ISA and Update RteCallRet->

Description:
The following executions flow, described in the SWDD, shall be tested:
ActivityInitial -> Initialize watchdog variable to 0U -> Pet the Watchdog using RTE call -> Declare Local variable to store SSM state and Initialize RteCallRet to 1U ->
Is ASM_V_State_t not equal to ASM_INITIALISED? = True -> Read Master time reference value using Rte calll -> Is RteCallRet equals 0U? = True -> 
Is wait time counter expired? OR Is Master time not equal to 255? = True -> Initialize ASM Modue, Update ASM_V_State_t to ASM_INITIALISED  ->
Is ASM_V_State_t equals ASM_INITIALISED? = True -> Read SSM State using RTE call and Update RteCallRet -> Is RteCallRet equals 0U? = True ->
Is SSM in Running vision Mode? -> Read latest data from HCA and Update RteCallRet -> Is RteCallRet equals 0U? = True ->Load ASM FIFO with latest data received from HCA -> Read latest Data from ISA and Update RteCallRet->
Is RteCallRet equals 0U? = False -> Send ASM FIFO Data -> ActivityFinal
